                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090626-96-defend984 t18090626-96-punish574"></join>
               Confined Six Months in the House of Correction, and there kept to Hard Labour
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18090626-96-punish575" type="punishmentDescription">
