                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090626-96-defend984 t18090626-96-punish575"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
